name: The Cheetah Bike
description:
For decades, magazines have been the primary source of photo documentation for custom motorcycles, choppers and nearly anything else under the sun. Photographs from bike shows, rallies & even full spread features for certain builds. 

But we’ve watched the digital era grow exponentially as each website, blog & app develop into their own massive platform to showcase these builds and works of art to people across the world.

Today we move one step towards the future by allowing a chance for the public to own a piece of that art. This is our own spin at a digital recreation of our first motorcycle that we build from the ground up which is why we found this suitable as our genesis NFT.

Unapologetically, 
Unaffiliated
